  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.839,
    "endTime": 218.839,
    "text": "Percival!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.839,
    "endTime": 222.839,
    "text": "Now, I really wish I'd bought the three-pack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.839,
    "endTime": 233.839,
    "text": "Oh, man, I really should have ray-shielded that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.839,
    "endTime": 239.839,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.839,
    "endTime": 251.839,
    "text": "Are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.839,
    "endTime": 256.839,
    "text": "Fearme!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.839,
    "endTime": 264.839,
    "text": "Found this perfectly good robe just lying around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.839,
    "endTime": 265.839,
    "text": "Has one hole, right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.839,
    "endTime": 267.839,
    "text": "Hey, look what else I just found."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.839,
    "endTime": 268.839,
    "text": "My hoagie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.839,
    "endTime": 269.839,
    "text": "I would not eat that if I were you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.839,
    "endTime": 271.839,
    "text": "Come on, let's get off this battle station."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.839,
    "endTime": 272.839,
    "text": "But we don't have a ship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.839,
    "endTime": 274.839,
    "text": "I know where there's a bus pod."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.839,
    "endTime": 275.839,
    "text": "Peri, great work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.839,
    "endTime": 277.839,
    "text": "Hey, don't be a stranger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.839,
    "endTime": 279.839,
    "text": "You think maybe you could turn this thing over?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.839,
    "endTime": 281.839,
    "text": "All the blazer rushing to my head."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.839,
    "endTime": 284.839,
    "text": "Hey, it's Luke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.839,
    "endTime": 286.839,
    "text": "They must have got the plans."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.839,
    "endTime": 288.839,
    "text": "He should hit that exhaust port no problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.839,
    "endTime": 290.839,
    "text": "I mean, it's practically as big as a womp rat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.839,
    "endTime": 294.839,
    "text": "Yeah, we should probably get out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.839,
    "endTime": 296.839,
    "text": "Come on, the bus pod is right through here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.839,
    "endTime": 301.839,
    "text": "Wait, wait, wait, no, no, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.839,
    "endTime": 302.839,
    "text": "Oh, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.839,
    "endTime": 304.839,
    "text": "That was the last ship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.839,
    "endTime": 305.839,
    "text": "Yeah, we're toast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.839,
    "endTime": 309.839,
    "text": "Well, if we had to go out, at least it was for something we believe in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.839,
    "endTime": 314.839,
    "text": "My only regret is that I spent so much time on the wrong side."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.839,
    "endTime": 316.839,
    "text": "My only regret is that I ate that hoagie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.839,
    "endTime": 322.839,
    "text": "I guess if I have a regret, it's that I never got reunited with my sister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.839,
    "endTime": 324.839,
    "text": "She left Tatooine when I was just a baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.839,
    "endTime": 328.839,
    "text": "Phineas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.839,
    "endTime": 330.839,
    "text": "Candace?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.839,
    "endTime": 332.839,
    "text": "Oh, I can't believe it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.839,
    "endTime": 333.839,
    "text": "You've gotten so big."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.839,
    "endTime": 334.839,
    "text": "I didn't even recognize you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.839,
    "endTime": 335.839,
    "text": "Hey, wait a minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.839,
    "endTime": 336.839,
    "text": "Why is this guy hugging us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.839,
    "endTime": 337.839,
    "text": "Oh, this is Ferb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.839,
    "endTime": 338.839,
    "text": "He's our stepbrother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.839,
    "endTime": 339.839,
    "text": "Mom remarried?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.839,
    "endTime": 340.839,
    "text": "What happened to Dad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.839,
    "endTime": 342.839,
    "text": "Funny story, actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.839,
    "endTime": 343.839,
    "text": "He..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.839,
    "endTime": 354.839,
    "text": "Wow, that was close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.839,
    "endTime": 356.839,
    "text": "Thanks for coming back to get us, Isabella."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.839,
    "endTime": 358.839,
    "text": "Well, that's what friends are for."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.839,
    "endTime": 363.839,
    "text": "Oh, but what about all those innocent baristas and bank tellers and bowling alley attendants?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.839,
    "endTime": 364.839,
    "text": "They're fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.839,
    "endTime": 366.839,
    "text": "The Firestar girls got them out earlier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.839,
    "endTime": 369.839,
    "text": "Okay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.839,
    "endTime": 376.839,
    "text": "Ah, Agent P."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.839,
    "endTime": 382.839,
    "text": "With you stopping Darth and Schmertz and the Rebellion destroying the Death Star, this day will be long remembered."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.839,
    "endTime": 391.839,
    "text": "Apparently, there are still copies of the Death Star plans out there somewhere, so still might have a teeny problem there, but we'll blow up that battle station when we come to it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.839,
    "endTime": 392.839,
    "text": "Hologram out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.839,
    "endTime": 399.839,
    "text": "So long, Perry the Platypus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.839,
    "endTime": 401.839,
    "text": "Now I can live to fight in the sequel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.839,
    "endTime": 410.839,
    "text": "I probably should have thought this one through better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.839,
    "endTime": 416.839,
    "text": "I didn't realize the escape pod would be platypus-sized, but plus, I'm sitting on the keys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.839,
    "endTime": 420.839,
    "text": "There's a hundred and four days of summer vacation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.839,
    "endTime": 423.839,
    "text": "And school comes along just to end it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.839,
    "endTime": 426.839,
    "text": "So the annual problem for our generation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.839,
    "endTime": 427.839,
    "text": " Is finding a good..."
  }
]